rows.label: tlk70000069_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I think there's still a ton of
treasure out here in Dannagh
Desert, just waiting to be found...

rows.label: tlk70000069_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I've been thinking about hiring
an adventurer with a taste for
mining to help me find some.

rows.label: tlk70000069_02_msg0003
rows.name:
You guys had a Blade that was
good at mining, didn't you?

rows.label: tlk70000069_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If so, I think you'll be able to find
lots of buried treasure. Not just here,
but in all sorts of other places, too.

rows.label: tlk70000069_02_msg0005
rows.name:
If I find any treasure before
you, though, don't think I'm
just going to hand it over!
